This map is my first release for BCS studios (studio 1000).
This took me 3 loong weeks of work and it was all worth it. I made it for gungame but feel free to use it as you wish.
Please note this map is still in beta but it is playable and fun :D.
If you find any bugs please PM me so i can fix them.

gratz to:
Kat.Fish for great help in some aspects of the map
